   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-accepting-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-accepting-b" mid="9" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Then his body should be claimed and laid to rest properly.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="8"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>I know you defeated Burnessa, but the Forest of Death remains very contaminated, so there will be resurrection of the dead from time to time.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-accepting-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-accepting-c" mid="11" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="10"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>Yes, I should be going there to retrieve him back, but I could not seem to get close to the forest</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-accepting-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-accepting-d" mid="13" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>How does the body purification works?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="12"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>I could not endure the poison cloud. But you, {user_nick}, seems to be able to withstand that kind of gas. So please could you go to the Forest of Death and purify Priest William's remains?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-accepting-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-accepting-e" mid="15" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>What to do?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="14"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>Purification ritual for the body seems complicated, requires quite a number of steps. However I am sure there will be shortcuts here and there..</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-accepting-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-accepting-f" mid="17" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html> Yes, I'll do it. </html>]]></talk_answer>
